  "notes": {
    "en": "Critical: fresh cells, do NOT over-lyse. Nucleosomal laddering = good library. 9-12 PCR cycles typical. ≥50M reads/sample.",
    "zh": "关键：新鲜细胞，不可过度裂解。核小体梯度条带 = 文库合格。通常 9-12 轮 PCR。≥50M reads/样品。"
